    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Odkaz</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body"><a href="https://darcakrvi.sk/" class="govuk-link" title="https://darcakrvi.sk/" target="_blank">https://darcakrvi.sk/</a></p>

    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Správca</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body">Aston ITM</p>

    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Dodávateľ</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body">Aston ITM</p>
